-1202632782/</ref>\n|}\n\n==Talent agency==\nHBMC manages over 100 Chinese A-list celebrities of movie, music and TV. [[Xun Zhou]], [[Angelababy]], [[Chen Kun (actor)|Kun Chen]], [[Zhao Wei]] and [[Shu Qi]] have appeared in Huayi productions.\n\n==See also==\n* [[C-pop]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Official website|http://huayi.sina.com.cn/}} {{in lang|zh}}\n\n{{Film distributors of China}}\n{{Film production companies of China}}\n\n[[Category:Chinese record labels]]\n[[Category:Talent agencies of mainland China]]\n[[Category:Pop record labels]]\n[[Category:Sibling filmmakers]]\n[[Category:Companies established in 1994]]\n[[Category:1994 establishments in China]]\n[[Category:Film production companies of China]]\n[[Category:Companies based in Beijing]]\n[[Category:Companies listed on the Shenzhen Stock Exchange]]\n[[Category:Chinese brands]]\n[[Category:Entertainment companies of China]]\n[[Category:Television production companies of China]]\n[[Category:Cinemas and movie theaters in China]]\n", "name_user": "190.234.106.57", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Huayi_Brothers"}
